/// =============================================================================
/// scr_p2p_config
/// =============================================================================
/// Required macros for the P2P rollback example.
/// Add this as a Script in your GameMaker project.
///
/// NOTE: If you already have VERB_UP/DOWN/LEFT/RIGHT or SIGNAL_ROLLBACK
/// defined elsewhere in your project, skip the duplicates here.
/// =============================================================================

// --- Input verb indices (must match your Input 10 profile) ---
#macro VERB_UP	0
#macro VERB_DOWN  1
#macro VERB_LEFT  2
#macro VERB_RIGHT 3

